name: SupplyRequest
title: SupplyRequest
publisher: Health Level Seven International (Orders and Observations)
description: A record of a request for a medication, substance or device used in the healthcare setting.

elements.name: SupplyRequest
elements.description: A record of a request for a medication, substance or device used in the healthcare setting.

elements.name: identifier
elements.description: Business identifiers assigned to this SupplyRequest by the author and/or other systems.

elements.name: category
elements.description: Category of supply, e.g. central, non-stock, etc.

elements.name: priority
elements.description: Indicates how quickly this SupplyRequest should be addressed with respect to other requests.

elements.name: itemCodeableConcept
elements.description: The item that is requested to be supplied.

elements.name: itemReference
elements.description: The item that is requested to be supplied.

elements.name: quantity
elements.description: The amount that is being ordered of the indicated item.

elements.name: parameter
elements.description: Specific parameters for the ordered item.

elements.name: occurrenceDateTime
elements.description: When the request should be fulfilled.

elements.name: occurrencePeriod
elements.description: When the request should be fulfilled.

elements.name: occurrenceTiming
elements.description: When the request should be fulfilled.

elements.name: requester
elements.description: The device, practitioner, etc. who initiated the request.

elements.name: supplier
elements.description: Who is intended to fulfill the request.

elements.name: reasonCode
elements.description: The reason why the supply item was requested.

elements.name: reasonReference
elements.description: The reason why the supply item was requested.

elements.name: deliverFrom
elements.description: Where the supply is expected to come from.

elements.name: deliverTo
elements.description: Where the supply is destined to go.
